OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain slowly
OL,6,Fclearing Scotland. Heavy, possibly
OL,7,Fthundery, showers cross the southeast
OL,8,Fin the second half of the night. Dry
OL,9,Fwith clear spells elsewhere. Warm, but
OL,10,Fslightly cooler than previous nights.
